%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant S as Skill
    participant Mem as AgentMemory
    participant F as Figma
    participant FS as FileSystem
    participant Preview as PreviewApp

    note over S,Preview: Phases 0,1,1.5,4,5 — follow create-component.mmd
    note over S,Preview: This diagram shows Sciter-specific overrides only

    note over S: Step 0 additions

    S->>F: get_code_connect_suggestions(nodeId, fileKey)
    F-->>S: mainComponentNodeId

    alt nodeId is a variant (mainComponentNodeId ≠ nodeId)
        S-->>U: STOP — variant node detected (◆)<br/>Provide the parent ◆◆ component set URL
        U-->>S: parent URL
        S->>S: re-parse fileKey + nodeId
    end

    note over S: Phase 0.5 — Variant Analysis and Plan (see create-component.mmd)

    S->>Mem: read .claude/agent-memory/sciter-create-component/feedback_*.md
    Mem-->>S: known fixes (typography, icon centering, layout tips)

    opt memory directory absent or empty
        S->>Mem: seed feedback_ssim_typography.md
    end

    note over S: Phase 1 — Agent 3 Sciter override

    note over S: after generic token + mixin matching:
    S->>FS: scan @font-face / font-loader for loaded font files
    FS-->>S: loaded weights list

    opt resolved mixin uses unloaded font weight
        S-->>U: mixin found but font file missing<br/>use fallback mixin or add font file?
        U-->>S: choice
    end

    note over S: Phase 2 Stream B — Sciter CSS/JS rules
    note over S: dip units 1:1 from Figma px (never px)<br/>flow: horizontal | vertical (not display: flex)<br/>width: * (not flex: 1) · overflow: none<br/>@mixin typography-name; (no font shorthand with var())<br/>no comma in @mixin values<br/>class Name extends Element · class not className<br/>__DIR__ + "img/..." icon paths · imports need .js extension
    note over S: apply known fixes from agent memory proactively

    note over S: Phase 3 — adapter.visual_verify() expansion

    note over S: resolve adaptive SSIM threshold
    S->>Mem: scan feedback_*.md for pattern matching component traits<br/>(has SVG icons? has border-radius?)
    Mem-->>S: matched ceiling (e.g. 0.92) or default 0.95

    S->>FS: tools/fetch-figma-screenshot.sh <fileKey> <nodeId> /tmp/figma-<name>.png
    FS-->>S: PNG at 2x scale, absolute bounds
    S->>FS: copy → tools/ScreenshotHistory/{ts}_figma_{name}.png

    loop max 3 attempts
        S->>Preview: tools/preview-component.sh <preview.js> <Name> <width> /tmp/figma-<name>.png
        note over Preview: internally: captures screenshot + runs find-component.py --direct
        note over Preview: window stays open — Space toggles Figma overlay
        Preview-->>S: SSIM score + /tmp/component-compare.png + /tmp/component-diff.png

        alt SSIM >= threshold (0.92–0.95 from memory)
            note over S: PASS — exit loop
        else SSIM < threshold
            S-->>U: show diff + score + region description
            U-->>S: explanation of discrepancy
            S->>FS: apply targeted CSS/JS fix
        end
    end

    alt passed (SSIM >= 0.95)
        S->>FS: copy preview screenshot → ScreenshotHistory/{ts}_code_{name}.png

        opt fix was applied during retries
            S->>Mem: write feedback_ssim_<topic>.md
        end
    else EC14 — still < 0.95 after 3 attempts
        S-->>U: Level 1 — side-by-side + SSIM progression + region delta
        U-->>S: explanation

        alt fix resolves the issue
            S->>FS: apply fix, re-run SSIM once
            S->>Mem: write feedback_ssim_<topic>.md
        else systematic pattern
            S-->>U: Level 2 — draft rule change proposal (show only — do not write)
        end

        opt tool limitation or script bug
            S-->>U: Level 3 — structured bug report<br/>component accepted: status needs-review
        end

        S->>FS: copy preview screenshot → ScreenshotHistory/{ts}_code_{name}.png
    end
